4,"uid":57394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2467b095ad492e24375befe0dae8ddee774bdd85","tid":56534,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"樓主教精你啦, 攬住成組一齊炒, <br />\n你既競爭對手就少左3個, 而陪你攞1既就多左3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條數你都識計啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要點做到? 首先千奇唔好爆粗, <br />\n因為你一爆粗考官就知你有心玩野, 有機會直接比晒5**你既組員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你只要一開波搶發言, 讀晒佢比你果篇ARTICLE 就達成一半任務 <br />\n有人同你爭唔緊要, 同佢鬥大聲鬥長氣根本無得輸 <br />\n<br />\n之後都要比人講下野既, 但要做到攬炒, 一定唔可以比佢地完完整整咁發言 <br />\n係佢地講左一兩句之後即刻大力點頭, 跟手大嗌 'YES! I AGREE WITH YOU!' <br />\n之後另轉頭問第個 'HOW ABOUT YOU?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ' <br />\n重覆多幾次, 你既任務已經成功, 可以對住個CAMERA問 'CAN I GO TO TOILET PLEASE?' <br />\n就可以起身走人, 費事完場比人圍住黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多位無心戀戰既巴打, 以你地一己之力拖死晒果堆平時睇你地唔起既名校精英, 絕對係學海生涯上最有意義既一件壯舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6513584c7dcd55bbc2ff1593bcf9f913932dd12","tid":56534,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考作文 一開始就叫加紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠 睇錯題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錯唔哂 都擾到敵嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 格離D人都嚇一嚇心諗考口試加咩紙"},{"pid":"97ee6399c7d50fd6af358f2634a607bd2cde2aee","tid":56534,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"賴左屎入去考"},{"pid":"4d6fd95202011c5c0df8d8482b34596014322ecf","tid":56534,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"