plyTime":"2016-12-27T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/215653_549b848ae3fd3851773756d83ed5d015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F215653_549b848ae3fd3851773756d83ed5d015.jpg&h=e1eb3f60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6310dc65d742a8a7b631f094bcca3aebe4ef31a9","tid":56534,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"總結時大叫微臣董昭先行告退<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20bf0c8f6c34ec6cb72301ea954b4846a59140b","tid":56534,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"報普通話<br />\n<br />\n狂講廣東話粗口"},{"pid":"1df918fc80a64f901a4cb2f25b39d5cd42c02ee2","tid":56534,"uid":45990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"其實有冇一早考完dse既巴打專登報2017口試玩野拉低其他人啲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd61638de3dd21eaea8e413ca706172f058912ef","tid":56534,"uid":45990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"擾敵呢樣野呢 就睇對手架姐<br />\n如果佢係男你又係男<br />\n一開波坐落去就對住佢打眼色<br />\n打3下 代表今晚食三哥<br />\n然後打2下 做個交叉手勢<br />\n代表2Q不收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢俾你迷惑到既時候你已經贏左一半<br />\n呢個時候你只要拉低啲你條褲既拉鏈<br />\n咁佢一定忍唔住 追住你條鳩嚟含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟到呢步唔洗講啦<br />\n順住個勢食埋其他組員同考官<br />\n保證你5星星之外其他人u曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6302c42dacc263582f183ac29c5c22c1a4d5c802","tid":56534,"uid":3719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"一坐低對住個cam講<br />\nBen,Why are you recording ?"},{"pid":"421de96668c8259030c722bf6f0e8d442a282893","tid":56534,"uid":51134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c